Uses of Package
com.ulflander.application.model

Packages that use com.ulflander.application.model
com.ulflander Main package for Minethat services. 
com.ulflander.application.model This classes are the internal model of document, tokens and so on in Minethat java services. 
com.ulflander.application.model.storage Storage utilities for models. 
com.ulflander.mining Tools dedicated to text mining, used either by Services or by Processors. 
com.ulflander.mining.nlp Contains utilities for Natural Language Processing related tasks. 
com.ulflander.mining.processors Contains abstract and concrete processors. 
com.ulflander.mining.processors.augment Processors that add more information onto a text: (geolocation, annotations...). 
com.ulflander.mining.processors.augment.geoloc Processors dedicated to geolocation. 
com.ulflander.mining.processors.augment.social Contains social related processors and dependencies. 
com.ulflander.mining.processors.extract Processors that extract and format document into an analyzable model. 
com.ulflander.mining.processors.extract.en Extraction processors dedicated to English language. 
com.ulflander.mining.processors.load Processors that save model, documents and analysis results in a location. 
com.ulflander.mining.processors.preset The package regroups everything about preset of processors. 
 

Classes in com.ulflander.application.model used by com.ulflander
Document
          Document is the main model in processing.
Job
          A model holds information about documents to be processed, processors to run on them or presets of processors to use, and also about the customer that initiated the model.
